{"tid":1669941,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（Mon post共狗話俾你老細知）抗爭唔會因為換特首而完結！！！","createTime":"2019-10-22T23:54:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T07:04:46.000Z","uid":50983,"like":117,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"27a05fa6a343fa168ed1003c710ffe1b07e08920","tid":1669941,"uid":50983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T23:54:13.000Z","msg":"用外媒放風話換特首<br />\n又做埋呢啲小動作<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">識唔識睇五大訴求？</span><br />\n仲有話要換特首咩？<br />\n唔好諗住扮讓步然後話好無奈香港抗爭者唔退一步<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家同定身邊嘅淺黃、中立派講清楚<br />\n對準政權唔係對準林鄭<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">即使佢下台，死傷被囚嘅義士唔會突然無事<br />\n係中共唔俾香港約定咗嘅民主、承諾咗嘅自由</span><br />\n就算邊個做特首都係一樣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">只要無民主自由，香港人都唔會停止抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光 復 香 港 ， 時 代 革 命 ！</span></span>"},{"pid":"21920eb041aca69aff24ba0c303bdcd52bdc872d","tid":1669941,"uid":50983,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T23:55:32.000Z","msg":"最好全香港一起身就有共識<br />\n<br />\n我地唔會後退"},{"pid":"05f73ee60576a23441915634485e0de94f3e4f15","tid":1669941,"uid":279874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T23:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2559d0031fb47c8d34b1cfa5e7f03d84a3bf4abc","tid":1669941,"uid":154187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T23:56:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5591192b034925f5bc144c90dfb6f8882